    "description": "JTEC Corporation engages in the technical staff intellectual property leasing business for engineers in Japan and internationally. It specializes in the dispatch of engineers to the development and design departments of manufacturing companies. It also operates in human resource businesses, nursing care businesses, event businesses, and posting businesses. The group focuses on recruitment, human resource development, and sales as the main pillars of sustainable business development. It provides services in areas requiring advanced skills, such as mechanical design, electrical and electronic design, and software, and is involved in research and development and design in four fields, including architectural design. The company also offers reskilling and re-career development services, technical education, and comprehensive career support, including compliance, ethics, and mental health. It serves manufacturing companies and other business clients in Japan. The company was incorporated in 1996 and is based in Chuo, Japan."
